videos.headline: Aggies with huge interception in the end zone
videos.description: Armani Watts climbs the ladder and comes down with stunning interception in the back of the end zone.

videos.headline: Perine notches 1st TD of first half
videos.description: Lamical Perine fights for extra yards and bulldozes his way into the end zone to give Florida the lead.

videos.headline: Texas A&M coach Sumlin needs better run game
videos.description: Head coach Kevin Sumlin says the Aggies offense looks to get the run game going and throw some more deep balls in the second half.

videos.headline: Mond keeps and scores for A&M
videos.description: Kellen Mond runs straight up the hole and is able to fight his way in for the score from 9 yards out.

videos.headline: Franks breaks free for huge gain
videos.description: Feleipe Franks scrambles out of the pocket and ends up evading tackles and gaining 79 yards putting the Gators in great field position.

videos.headline: Massey's TD run gives Gators the lead
videos.description: Dre Massey dives into the corner of the end zone early in the fourth quarter to give Florida the lead.

videos.headline: Dodson INT secures victory for Aggies
videos.description: Feleipe Franks has an opportunity to drive the Gators downfield with under a minute, but Tyrel Dodson seals the victory with the interception for Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Mond: We know how to fight 'til the end
videos.description: WR Christian Kirk believed in the Aggies pulling out the victory and is ready for the weeks ahead.

videos.headline: Breaking down the Aggies victory in the swamp
videos.description: Beth Mowins and Anthony Becht dissect what it took for Texas A&M to pull out the win in Florida.

videos.headline: Texas A&M knocks off Florida in the Swamp
videos.description: In a defensive struggle, Tyrel Dodson's late interception on Feleipe Franks seals the deal on Texas A&M's 19-17 victory over Florida.
